1. *Zamolila* sam te da mi pomogneš oko pripreme večere. (I asked you to help me with dinner preparation.)
2. Ona *zamolila* svoje roditelje za novac. (She asked her parents for money.)
3. Kada budeš odlazio, *zamoli* ga da mi javi. (When you leave, ask him to let me know.)
4. Ja sam joj *zamolila* da mi pozajmi knjigu. (I asked her to lend me a book.)
5. *Zamolili* smo ih da nas sačekaju ispred pozorišta. (We asked them to wait for us in front of the theater.)
6. Nisam želela da idem sama, pa sam ga *zamolila* da me isprati. (I didn't want to go alone, so I asked him to accompany me.)
7. Moja sestra je *zamolila* da joj donesemo kafu. (My sister asked us to bring her coffee.)
8. Kada budeš dolazio, *zamoli* komšiju da ti pomogne oko prenošenja stvari. (When you come, ask the neighbor to help you with moving things.)
9. Ona me je *zamolila* da joj čuvam dete dok ona ode u kupovinu. (She asked me to babysit her child while she goes shopping.)
10. *Zamolite* lekara da vam prepiše antibiotik. (Ask the doctor to prescribe you an antibiotic.)